value: Breeds is. off New Zealand; ranges to se Australia and Vanuatu

Breeds on islets off North Island and in Cook Strait, New Zealand. Migratory: ranges south and east to Banks Peninsula, South Island, and Chatham Islands, and west to southern Australia in winter. Stragglers recorded from New Caledonia and New Hebrides.
